description: Mausam Curry N Bites is an authentic Indian cuisine. Our food is known for its great savory flavor and spices. We were ranked number one by New York Street Food and Zagat for our famous Chicken Tikka Masala which is composed of tomatoes cream base sauce. CBS news coverage of our Chicken Korma (cashew base sweet). Our famous bites are known for Samosa/ Kati Roll/ Chaat vegetarian, non-vegetarian and vegan.
name: Mausam Curry N Bites
